name: drone-object-detection-using-haar-cascades
description: For my bachelor thesis @KULeuven campus Bruges, I have to develop drone-vision based software which should be able to detect cross-objects, and detect the correct cross based upon color clustering. If an object has been detected, a direction needs to be returned to another script, which controls a drone.
